{"tid":1427270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日admin風向統計有問題","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:06:05.000Z","uid":76216,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d87036ba4b5930417678222afa0699bcd9388eae","tid":1427270,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:35:14.000Z","msg":"回應會員對本討論區評分系統及對管理團隊的各種查詢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1424552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1424552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nadmin提到，p牌正洗負評比例唔高，主要係舊會員投票，所以唔存在p牌帶風向投票。<br />\n<br />\n其實咁嘅推論係錯的，因為你提出嘅data只係<br />\n（結果）而唔係一個有時序嘅統計，因為有可能就係因為一開po，幾百p牌入去洗評價，其後舊會員見到就會羊群心理跟住岩岩所見嘅正負評比例去投票。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">只用（結果）去推論的話，其實仲可以話3毛用幾百人就帶動幾千舊會員風向。</span><br />\n<br />\n要真係排除唔係有p牌帶風向，可以用時序統計黎睇，例如 開po後30分鐘做統計，幾多人投正負評，1個鐘頭之後又係幾多，咁先睇到個發展曲線，咁個統計先有意義，<span style=\"color: maroon;\">只用結果黎推論判斷係十分錯誤！！</span>"},{"pid":"0fb465c034a6d9540bbe9ec7799dd82d50b72c4a","tid":1427270,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee66c2d4050b110e2a06de9f60ca6ec4a4c54f3d","tid":1427270,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a052dbf50e03875d20821ae0282e16892dffcc8","tid":1427270,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaefb249e5771cf5f3e85c1a70a69762a0b6f82","tid":1427270,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0849e97c325